Hello! My name is Rhylie Ladoucer and I am an undergrad at Clemson University
studying genetics and biochemistry. I am currently in the process of
developing a custom social media scraper for Dr. Ennis's Creative Inquiry
involved in debunking pseudoscience and exposing the predatory 
tactics of the wellness industry. Thank you for taking the time to
look through my code! 

This is a work in progress, so you may see some unfinished or nonfunctional
code. I'm mainly using this repo as a means of tracking my progress. 